# Keep the image lean AND keep secrets out of it. Key material and .env files are passed
# to the hosted loop as runtime secrets (fly secrets set / railway variables), NEVER baked.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/dist
**/.git
**/secret
**/*.pem
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/audit
web
mcp
bot
signal-service
_design_import
contracts/target
contracts/src
**/*.orig.wasm
